.SS get_public_key
.IX Subsection "get_public_key"
.Vb 1
\&        $pubkey = $obj\->get_public_key()
.Ve
.PP
This method generates a new NUMS public key and returns it as an instance of
Bitcoin::Crypto::Key::Public.
.PP
Note that calling this method repeatedly without modifying "tweak"
will keep yielding the same public key.
